sequenceDiagram
    participant Angular as Angular App<br/>localhost:4200
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant CORS as CORS Filter
    participant AuthCtrl as AuthController
    participant UserSvc as UserService
    participant SessionSvc as SessionService
    participant TokenProv as BearerTokenProvider
    participant UserRepo as UserRepository
    participant SessionRepo as SessionRepository
    participant H2 as H2 Database
    
    Angular->>Browser: POST /api/auth/login<br/>{email, pingSsoId, name, picture}
    Browser->>CORS: HTTP Request
    Note over CORS: Check CORS<br/>Origin: localhost:4200
    CORS->>AuthCtrl: Forward Request
    
    AuthCtrl->>UserSvc: createOrUpdateUser(email, name, picture, pingSsoId)
    UserSvc->>UserRepo: findByEmail(email) OR create new
    UserRepo->>H2: Query/Insert User
    H2-->>UserRepo: User Object
    UserRepo-->>UserSvc: User
    UserSvc-->>AuthCtrl: User (with id)
    
    AuthCtrl->>UserSvc: recordLogin(userId, ipAddress)
    UserSvc->>UserSvc: Update lastLoginIp & lastLoginTime
    UserSvc->>UserRepo: save(user)
    UserRepo->>H2: Update User
    
    AuthCtrl->>SessionSvc: createSession(user, request)
    SessionSvc->>SessionSvc: Generate sessionId (UUID)
    SessionSvc->>SessionSvc: Set createdAt, expiresAt, ipAddress
    SessionSvc->>SessionRepo: save(session)
    SessionRepo->>H2: Insert Session
    H2-->>SessionRepo: Session (with id)
    SessionRepo-->>SessionSvc: Session
    SessionSvc-->>AuthCtrl: Session
    
    AuthCtrl->>TokenProv: generateToken(email, claims)
    TokenProv->>TokenProv: Create JWT Token<br/>claims: userId, roles
    TokenProv-->>AuthCtrl: bearerToken (JWT)
    
    AuthCtrl->>AuthCtrl: setSessionCookie(response, sessionId)
    Note over AuthCtrl: Create ResponseCookie<br/>HttpOnly=true<br/>Secure=true<br/>SameSite=Strict
    
    AuthCtrl->>AuthCtrl: Build Response DTO
    Note over AuthCtrl: {<br/>  success: true,<br/>  user: User object,<br/>  sessionId: string,<br/>  bearerToken: JWT,<br/>  expiresAt: datetime,<br/>  tokenType: "Bearer",<br/>  expiresIn: 86400<br/>}
    
    AuthCtrl-->>Browser: HTTP 200 OK<br/>+ Set-Cookie header<br/>+ Response Body
    Browser-->>Angular: Response + Cookie
    Angular->>Angular: Store bearerToken<br/>Store sessionId<br/>Redirect to dashboard
